subject: Preakness Stakes
Triple Crown (Horse Racing)
Horse Racing
lead_paragraph: Lookin at Lucky’s Preakness Stakes victory on Saturday attracted an average of 8.4 million viewers on NBC, down 23 percent from the 10.9 million who watched the filly Rachel Alexandra’s win last year.
